Definition: the state of being contented with your situation in life
Example: he relaxed in sleepy contentedness; they could read to their heart's content
Synonyms: adj, all, contented, content, verb, emotion, consumption, acceptance, the, state, of, being, with, your, situation, in, life, he, relaxed, sleepy, they, could, read, to, their, heart, s
Category: noun.state
